{
  "texts": [
    "Key questions include: (RQ1): How reliable are LLMs in the context of analog circuit design, and what are their foundational limitations in this domain?",
    "(RQ2): What steps are required to develop a specialized LLM tailored specifically for analog circuit design?",
    "(RQ3): How can the challenge of data scarcity be addressed in the niche field of analog circuit design?",
    "(RQ4): Are there methodologies that would enable LLMs to autonomously generate or enhance datasets needed for analog circuit design?",
    "(RQ5): How can LLMs be equipped with logical reasoning capabilities specific to circuit design to ensure effective interpretation and solution of hardware-specific problems?"
  ]
}